item.title: CVE-2023-27510|2024-08-02T12:16:35.363Z -- jubei%20inc. -- jb%20inquiry%20form
item.description: JB Inquiry form contains an exposure of private personal information to an unauthorized actor vulnerability, which may allow a remote unauthenticated attacker to obtain information entered from forms created using the affected product. The affected products and versions are as follows: JB Inquiry form versions 0.6.1 and 0.6.0, JB Inquiry form versions 0.5.2, 0.5.1 and 0.5.0, and JB Inquiry form version 0.40.
